      "content": "but it doesn't feel like a clean slate. it feels like the substance is just gone. like the paint dried up and cracked, and there's nothing underneath the surface anymore. just... nothing. why would i want to be a vessel if there's nothing left to put in it? it just feels heavy and pointless.",
